403, 107.6776, 107.2675, 106.8635, 108.1089, 107.0326, 107.1251, 105.4808, 104.411, 106.3616, 106.5636, 107.696, 107.4374, 107.3117, 108.5216, 108.4018, 108.4881, 109.6753, 110.8581, 110.8854, 111.6987, 110.4907, 111.2495, 110.1241, 109.4483, 109.1867, 108.7282, 109.5864, 109.8029, 110.9461, 110.3368, 110.1514, 108.5386, 108.7456, 109.1387, 108.8741, 109.5115, 110.4301, 109.5522, 109.9252, 111.6984, 110.2489, 110.854, 111.0063, 110.1336, 111.2324, 109.3313, 108.2024, 108.8385, 108.0139, 108.5743, 108.8948, 107.6528, 109.4611, 108.2784, 106.4395, 107.4684, 104.4888, 104.1125, 105.7317, 105.3699, 105.9683, 105.4304, 106.428, 106.7843, 107.3336, 107.4891, 107.5034, 107.6397, 106.8207, 109.2969, 109.3791, 107.5805, 107.8455, 108.5055, 108.6817, 108.1432, 108.2216, 108.4074, 110.2885, 110.4163, 111.3896, 112.1606, 113.1573, 114.6612, 115.6946, 116.5626, 115.5915, 116.507, 115.9983, 116.3185, 115.7055, 116.7834, 118.5116, 117.734, 118.5449, 116.6726, 116.6828, 117.1322, 120.2708, 120.1642, 119.5057, 121.1928, 121.5986, 122.5807, 128.869, 133.6989, 132.6845, 132.7701, 133.7412, 135.6446, 134.8533, 136.1571, 136.6739, 135.06, 133.4425, 134.1596, 134.3049, 134.0499, 132.704, 132.1393, 132.8871, 134.3637, 135.3285, 133.9826, 133.8629, 134.9253, 134.4138, 135.3282, 137.2321, 138.7777, 140.0264, 139.3071, 137.3356, 137.9647, 139.6937, 139.7337, 138.4569, 137.137, 137.6065, 138.2159, 137.2973, 136.7027, 138.6374, 138.3027, 139.7764, 139.68, 144.0032, 144.1287, 144.9147, 147.6347, 148.9642, 151.2274, 148.2934, 144.947, 145.6381, 144.9594, 147.8954, 149.4292, 149.465, 149.3247, 148.9161, 148.1452, 148.7792, 148.2147, 148.9713, 151.8725, 152.679, 150.7504, 148.9834, 149.4112, 151.2983, 152.4126, 153.6096, 153.8192, 152.9145, 153.3114, 154.6529, 155.6366, 153.1448, 154.7705, 156.0878, 155.7703, 157.1318, 160.1998, 155.7728, 153.0363, 153.5266, 153.655, 153.0238, 152.9468, 153.2894, 153.2561, 153.1561, 153.1393, 154.0316, 153.6064, 153.103, 153.6848, 154.4432, 153.933, 151.3052, 152.6687, 151.9259, 149.3021, 148.9972, 149.6838, 147.4094, 148.6626, 146.8353, 149.3146, 148.657, 147.9662, 147.8385, 148.5448, 148.2274, 147.9418, 148.896, 149.6389, 149.0308, 149.8254, 151.0137, 151.0148], "summary_html": "<h1>商品期货因子策略之资金流向</h1>\n<p><strong>Sharpe 1.08 (扣费后) | 通过</strong></p>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略基于中信期货研报中的资金流向因子概念，使用 <code>memberdiff20</code>（前20名期货席位净持仓差）作为机构资金流向的日频代理指标。研报原文使用 tick 级数据计算资金流向（通过盘口信息区分主动买卖），但我们没有 tick 数据，因此使用席位持仓差（直接反映大资金的多空方向变化）作为等价替代。</p>\n<p>核心发现：与研报中资金流向的\"反直觉\"（contrarian）逻辑不同，<code>memberdiff20</code> 在<strong>动量方向</strong>更有效——当机构资金持续净流入某品种时（cumulative memberdiff20 上升），该品种未来倾向于继续上涨。这与席位持仓的性质一致：大机构的持仓变化具有信息优势和领先性，而非简单的\"过度拥挤\"。策略通过截面排名将品种分为多空组合，定期再平衡并进行波动率目标缩放。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>核心信号为 <code>memberdiff20</code> 的 N 日滚动累积和：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{CumMD20}_{i,t} = \\sum_{k=t-N+1}^{t} \\text{memberdiff20}_{i,k}</div>\n<p>截面排名转连续仓位：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{cs\\_rank}(\\text{CumMD20}_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = (\\text{rank}_{i,t} - 0.5) \\times 2</div>\n<p>波动率目标缩放：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{signal}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t}</span> 为过去60日已实现波动率。</p>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>lookback (N)</td><td>25</td><td>20-45</td><td>memberdiff20 滚动累加窗口</td></tr><tr><td>hold_days</td><td>20</td><td>15-25</td><td>再平衡间隔</td></tr><tr><td>vol_target</td><td>0.15</td><td>0.10-0.20</td><td>波动率目标</td></tr><tr><td>exclude_syms</td><td>SA,CF,SR,SM,YY</td><td>-</td><td>排除的弱势品种</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (扣费后)</td><td><strong>1.08</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>70.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动率</td><td>65.9%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-32.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手率</td><td>0.564</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>前3变体对比</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>最大回撤</th></tr><tr><td>md20_25_h20_ex_raw</td><td>1.08</td><td>70.9%</td><td>-32.3%</td></tr><tr><td>ema_md20_20_h15_ex_raw</td><td>1.05</td><td>69.7%</td><td>-31.1%</td></tr><tr><td>md20_25_h25_ex_raw</td><td>1.04</td><td>68.3%</td><td>-35.3%</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.15</td><td>0.66</td><td>0.96</td><td>1.20</td><td>0.72</td><td>1.48</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.00</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>R1</strong> (Sharpe 0.31): 初始实现3种资金流向proxy: (1) sign(ret)*|opi_chg|/volume, (2) memberdiff20 rolling sum, (3) opi_chg_rate*vol_surprise。全部使用contrarian方向。opiflow40_h20效果最好但依然很弱。问题：contrarian方向对proxy和md20可能不对；proxy formula用abs(opi_chg)丢失了方向信息。</li>\n<li><strong>R2</strong> (Sharpe 0.70): 关键转折。修正proxy formula去掉abs()，对memberdiff20同时测试momentum和contrarian方向。发现 <strong>memberdiff20 momentum方向</strong> (md20_40_h10_mom) Sharpe 0.70远超contrarian方向（-0.74）。Proxy因子全线负Sharpe。确认席位持仓差是领先指标而非拥挤度指标。</li>\n<li><strong>R3</strong> (Sharpe 0.77): 聚焦memberdiff20 momentum，window grid 20-80, hold grid 5-20。最优窗口收敛到30天/20天再平衡。加入OPI change momentum和combo变体作为辅助，但效果不如纯md20。2023年Sharpe -0.44仍是拖累。</li>\n<li><strong>R4</strong> (Sharpe 1.08): 精细grid围绕最优（window 25-45, hold 15-25），加入EMA平滑版本和vol_target 0.20变体。<strong>关键突破</strong>：排除5个持续亏损品种（SA/CF/SR/SM/YY）后Sharpe从0.77跃升至1.08，2023年从-0.44转正至0.72。所有年份均为正Sharpe。EMA版本同样表现出色（1.05）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（排除SA/CF/SR/SM/YY，约51个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 约20天换仓</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - memberdiff20 字段非空率约23%，仅2018年12月后数据较完整，回测区间约6年\n<p>- 与因子库中 guomao 因子相关性 0.75（likely_redundant），但Sharpe接近（1.08 vs 1.18） - 排除品种列表基于样本内表现，有过拟合风险 - 研报原文使用 tick 级资金流向数据，日频 proxy 无法完全复现原文的信号质量</p>"}